description.plain:
Darak Figueroa, (b. August 6, 2001), better known by his stage name StaySolidRocky, is an American rapper from Richmond, Virginia, born in San Antonio, Texas. Rocky’s best known for hit song “Party Girl,” which went viral on video sharing platform TikTok. The song caught the attention of rapper Lil Uzi Vert, who ended up remixing the song.

On July 17, 2020, Rocky released his debut EP titled Fallin' via Columbia Records.

songs.title: Party Girl

description.plain:
“Party Girl” is an ode to a girl, the titular “party girl”, who thoroughly enjoys drinking, doing drugs, and, of course, partying.

The song became notable for its inclusion in TikTok videos starting in May 2020. The song has been used in over 10,000,000 videos on the platform, and charted in the top 40 of the Billboard Hot 100 in late May 2020.
